Open the package;)
search for cape of dungeoonering.
now open up or model map in ur client
open the dungeoonering map and u will see
3 thing
2 models
1 int
copy the 2 models named 12555/12556
open up or model map in ur client again and add them to the model map;)
now open class8.java and do Ctrl-f and search for dragon claws under that u will add the ints from the dungeoonering cape and save it now
search for the compiller in the client map COMPILER.BAT click 2 times u see this
Compiling…
Note: Some input files use or override a deprecated API.
